  "titleCh": "阿美族蓋房子",
  "soundPath": null,
  "sentence": [
    {
      "chinese": "台灣各原住民族所建造的房子各有不同，例如阿美族人大多將房子蓋在平地上，利用就地的材料來建造，大多是以木材、竹子、茅草、藤類。",
      "ab": "Cowa kahecad ko pipatireng to loma’ ko Yincomin a finacadan no Taywan. Tinako, itiniay i dafdaf a patireng to loma’ ko no ’Amis. Palingata sanay a miala to kilang, ’awel, eli’ ato ’oway ko sapipatireng to loma’.",
